sox
-------------------------------------------
SoX (also known as Sound eXchange) translates sound files between
different file formats, and optionally applies various sound effects.

SoX is intended as the Swiss Army knife of sound processing tools.  It
doesn't do anything very well, but sooner or later it comes in very
handy.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  file-4.21-1
  libao2-0.8.8-3
  libavcodec52-17736-1
  libavformat52-17736-1
  libavutil49-17736-1
  libFLAC8-1.2.1-2
  libgsm0-1.0.12-1
  libid3tag0-0.15.1b-5
  libmad0-0.15.1b-5
  libmp3lame0-3.98.2-1
  libogg0-1.1.3-1
  libpng12-1.2.34-1
  libsamplerate0-0.1.7-1
  libsndfile1-1.0.17-2
  libvorbis0-1.2.0-2
  libvorbisenc2-1.2.0-2
  libvorbisfile3-1.2.0-2
  libwavpack1-4.50.1-1
  zlib-1.2.3-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.63-1
  automake1.10-1.10.1-2
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.4.3-1
  gawk-3.1.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  libtool-2.2.6a-1
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23a-2
