Canonical homepage:
  http://sox.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/sox/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack sox-14.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./sox-14.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libsox-devel-14.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libsox1-14.2.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/sox-14.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/sox-14.2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

